## Display & PDF parity

- **Single source**: `lib/maintenance/maintenanceDisplayFormat.ts` — `formatMaintenanceInteger` (en-AU grouping), `formatMaintenanceNumericField`, `buildDoorMetaSummaryLine` (subtitle **must match** PDF door meta). Change PDF + **`DoorInspectionCard`** together.

### Door meta line

- Omit empty segments; no door type for empty/`unspecified`; **no `Cycles:`** unless entered and &gt; 0 (no `N/A`). **View Window Visibility** when finite (including `0%`), grouped digits. PDF: draw meta line only when helper returns non-empty.

### Door notes (PDF)

- Empty notes: no dash placeholder; empty body under “Door Notes” is OK.

### pdf-lib text

- `drawText()` does not wrap `\n`; split on `\r?\n`, wrap with font metrics (e.g. `wrapPdfTextLines`). Do not hard-break by character count.

### Photo grid

- Thumbnail cap: **`PHOTO_THUMB_MAX_PT`** in `lib/pdf/layouts/maintenancePageMetrics.ts` (affects breaks/layout).

### Numeric fields (cycles / view window / CW / CH)

- **Cycles** & **View Window Visibility**: controlled display via `formatMaintenanceInteger`; store numeric from digits only. Do not mix `register()` + `onInput` that strips commas on controlled values. **CW/CH**: display `formatMaintenanceNumericField`; persist digits-only or null.

