## Client access & links

- Approved singles use `share_token`; viewer `/report/view/[token]` (merged or single).
- **Copy client link** = viewer URL from `maintenanceReportClientViewUrl` / `client_view_url` (`NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL` + `/report/view/{token}`), **not** raw Supabase `pdf_url`.
- Merged rows: viewer URL in `merged_reports.pdf_url`; singles expose `client_view_url` on `GET /api/maintenance/reports` and draft/approve responses.
- Portal **Download**: `GET /api/maintenance/pdf/[reportId]`; embed `coverQrPngBytes` when approved + `share_token` present.
- Schema: ensure migrations defining `share_token` / `approved` (e.g. `047_maintenance_reports_client_share`) are applied before relying on columns.

---

## Workflow emails

- Resolve labels via **`resolveClientLocationForReport`** when emails need client/site from `client_location_id`.
- **Client display name**: `clientNameFromDbRow` semantics — `clients` with `select('*')`; consider **`name`**, **`client_name`**, **`company_name`** (not only `name`/`company_name`) to avoid **Unknown Client**.
- **Location**: `locationLabelFromDbRow` aligned with PDF options (`buildMaintenancePdfOptions`).
- **Manager HTML**: do not prefix body with literal **Technician** before `technician_name` (avoids “Technician Technician”). Prefer **`<b>{technician_name}</b> submitted…**”; sign-off aligned with technician approval mail (**Thanks** / **NBE Team**).
